<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title || 'Lỗi' %></title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" />
  <style>
    .error-icon {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: #ef4444;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(239,68,68,0.12);
    }
    .error-card {
      max-width: 420px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      border: none;
    }
    .error-btn {
      min-width: 120px;
      font-weight: 500;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="min-height: 100vh;">
  <div class="card error-card p-4">
    <div class="text-center">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-exclamation error-icon"></i>
      <h3 class="text-danger mb-2">Đăng nhập thất bại!</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">Tài khoản hoặc mật khẩu không đúng.<br>Vui lòng thử lại hoặc đăng ký tài khoản mới.</p>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-between gap-2">
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary error-btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Đăng nhập</a>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-success error-btn">Đăng ký<i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus ms-2"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 